{"TopicId":204847,"ForumId":109,"TopicTitle":"Paying ?","CreatedByName":"over 360","CreatedById":216054,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T10:19:14Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"over 360","CreatedById":216054,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T10:19:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont\u003Eest ce que \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003Eles\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\u003Cfont\u003E\u00A0personnes ayant d\u00E9j\u00E0 payer le jeu devrons a nouveau le payer ?\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont\u003E[Translation]\u003Cbr\u003E\nwill people who have already paid for the game have to pay for it again?\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-15T10:24:29Z\u0022 title=\u002209/15/2021 10:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 15, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by James Kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded Translation\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T10:28:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/216054-over-360/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022216054\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/216054-over-360/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@over 360\u003C/a\u003E, a translation has been added to you post and title because all posts, outside of the international sub forums, require an English translation. This is because not all browsers and devices support automatic translation. We encourage you to use a service like google translate if you wish to post in the general forum.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Space Kerbalisation Tech","CreatedById":211297,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T10:33:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nksp2 is a separate game, so i imagine most users will have to pay for it again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"modus","CreatedById":207631,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T10:38:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSince you haven\u0027t paid for the game, you will have to pay for the game in order to play the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jastrone","CreatedById":208489,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T11:29:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyes its a new game. not an update to ksp. also most sales would be from ksp 1 players so there would be a loss in money for the company\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kapitalizing Every Word","CreatedById":212780,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T11:40:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe if you own the game you will have a discount? expect to pay something anyways because they need some money\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T11:52:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf they want it on different platforms, maybe, I\u0027ve done that with few games.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T12:50:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032086\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631701154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216054\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022over 360\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, over 360 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwill people who have already paid for the game have to pay for it again?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNobody already paid for the game, they aren\u0027t selling it yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T12:54:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSHUT UP INTERCEPT GAMES AND LET ME GIVE YOU MY MONEY!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mcwaffles2003","CreatedById":180102,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T13:09:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOui\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kapitalizing Every Word","CreatedById":212780,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T13:17:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032126\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631710221\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002268648\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Master39\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n26 minutes ago, Master39 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNobody already paid for the game, they aren\u0027t selling it yet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think he/she was talking about people who already paid KSP1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T13:31:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032148\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631711836\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212780\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kapitalizing Every Word\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Kapitalizing Every Word said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think he/she was talking about people who already paid KSP1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know, but since the dawn of videogames a sequel is not an update (except for sport games, but those suck by default) so the default state to give for granted is that if a new, different, studio comes up with a sequel a decade after the original game you have to expect to have to pay for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo the answer to \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E question is no, nobody will have to pay 2 times for either KSP1 or KSP2, they only have to pay once each if they want both.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"over 360","CreatedById":216054,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T17:52:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032157\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631712674\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002268648\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Master39\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nIl y a 4 heures, Master39 a dit :\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJe sais, mais depuis l\u2019aube des jeux vid\u00E9o, une suite n\u2019est pas une mise \u00E0 jour (sauf pour \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003Eles\u003C/abbr\u003E jeux de sport, mais ceux-ci sont nuls par d\u00E9faut), donc l\u2019\u00E9tat par d\u00E9faut \u00E0 donner pour acquis est que si un nouveau studio diff\u00E9rent propose une suite une d\u00E9cennie apr\u00E8s le jeu original, vous devez vous attendre \u00E0 devoir payer pour cela.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDonc, la r\u00E9ponse \u00E0 la question \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E est non, personne n\u2019aura \u00E0 payer 2 fois pour KSP1 ou KSP2, ils n\u2019ont \u00E0 payer qu\u2019une fois chacun s\u2019ils veulent \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003Eles\u003C/abbr\u003E deux.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmerci\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"over 360","CreatedById":216054,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-15T17:52:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032148\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631711836\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212780\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kapitalizing Every Word\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Kapitalizing Every Word said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJe pense qu\u2019il parlait de personnes qui payaient d\u00E9j\u00E0 KSP1\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\noui\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nmerci pour vos reponse\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthank you for your answers\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-15T20:32:41Z\u0022 title=\u002209/15/2021 08:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 15, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Vanamonde\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EPlease post in English when not using the International subforums.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-16T00:38:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032093\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631702031\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211297\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Space Kerbalisation Tech\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Space Kerbalisation Tech said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nksp2 is a separate game, so i imagine \u003Cstrong\u003Emost users\u003C/strong\u003E will have to pay for it again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll quickly jump in and say that no matter how early/late you got KSP 1. You HAVE TO PAY for KSP 2 FULL PRICE.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-16T00:54:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032462\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631752731\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211250\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Doodling Astronaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, The Doodling Astronaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll quickly jump in and say that no matter how early/late you got KSP 1. You HAVE TO PAY for KSP 2 FULL PRICE.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy\u00A0\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Ewouldn\u0027t\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003Ewe have to pay for a totally new game with totally new game features produced by a totally different production studio?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t imagine a scenario where you buy one product new and you keep getting newer versions of it for the rest of your life. It doesn\u0027t work for cars, computers (hello, Dell, about my free upgrade! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E) or cell phones. In fact, most gaming studios would have made us pay for multiple DLCs to get all the new parts we were given free between 1.0 to 1.12. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0has gone above and beyond what I could have ever asked for or thought any production company would offer.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll gladly pay full price for KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Greenfire32","CreatedById":36705,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-16T03:02:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemember when Halo came out and people bought it and then they made Halo 2 and people bought that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe audacity...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-16T03:23:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032462\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631752731\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211250\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Doodling Astronaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The Doodling Astronaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll quickly jump in and say that no matter how early/late you got KSP 1. You HAVE TO PAY for KSP 2 FULL PRICE.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I\u0027ll point out that \u0022most users\u0022 doesn\u0027t necessarily have anything to do with buying ksp1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere will be some people who get the game for free because they\u0027re big streamers, or get a code from a big streamer, or know Nate and ask him nicely or who knows what.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-16T09:57:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032510\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631762628\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nknow Nate and ask him nicely or who knows what.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d even more gladly pay full price. Why shouldn\u0027t anyone support their friends?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SciMan","CreatedById":12748,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-22T18:01:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew game, new development studio, no way in heck is anyone getting a discount.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course that\u0027s just my overly-cynical self talking, we might get a discount (it\u0027s not impossible) but I think it\u0027s very highly unlikely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: Oh yeah and I already bought KSP two times before, (once from Squad and once on Steam because Steam handles updates better, and I liked the game so much that I wanted to support the creators of it more).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-09-22T18:02:46Z\u0022 title=\u002209/22/2021 06:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 22, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by SciMan\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AtomicTech","CreatedById":210823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-22T18:18:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMan, I wish there were no limits on likes....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224035021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221632333694\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212748\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SciMan\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, SciMan said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNew game, new development studio, no way in heck is anyone getting a discount.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOf course that\u0027s just my overly-cynical self talking, we might get a discount (it\u0027s not impossible) but I think it\u0027s very highly unlikely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEDIT: Oh yeah and I already bought KSP two times before, (once from Squad and once on Steam because Steam handles updates better, and I liked the game so much that I wanted to support the creators of it more).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032593\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631786245\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/16/2021 at 4:57 AM, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d even more gladly pay full price. Why shouldn\u0027t anyone support their friends?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032510\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631762628\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Superfluous J\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/15/2021 at 10:23 PM, Superfluous J said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd I\u0027ll point out that \u0022most users\u0022 doesn\u0027t necessarily have anything to do with buying ksp1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere will be some people who get the game for free because they\u0027re big streamers, or get a code from a big streamer, or know Nate and ask him nicely or who knows what.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SciMan","CreatedById":12748,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-22T18:23:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh yeah, and if you have problems paying for KSP 2 on your own and you still live with your parents, you could always try explaining to them that it gives you \u0022hands-on\u0022 learning about rocket science and astrophysics, and I don\u0027t know of a (good) parent that would willingly prevent their child from learning things that could lead to a very high paying job (aerospace jobs are REALLY well paid).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-09-22T23:14:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224032086\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022204847\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221631701154\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022216054\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022over 360\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/15/2021 at 5:19 AM, over 360 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont\u003Ewill people who have already paid for the game have to pay for it again?\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, you don\u0027t have to pay for it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou only need to pay if you want to play it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}